            . I am a <rs id="t18321018-31-viclabel187" type="occupation">professor of languages</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-31-victim409 t18321018-31-viclabel187"></join>, and live in Berner-street. On the evening of the 22nd of September I was in <placeName id="t18321018-31-crimeloc188">Princes-street, Soho</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18321018-31-crimeloc188" type="placeName" value="Princes-street, Soho"></interp>
