                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-31-off185 t18321018-31-crimeloc188"></join>; I had a handkerchief in my pocket - I did not feel it taken, but the Policeman told me of it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321018-31-person411">
                  WILLIAM 
                  RICE
               <interp inst="t18321018-31-person411" type="surname" value="RICE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321018-31-person411" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321018-31-person411" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a porter. I happened to meet Hobbs in Princes-street; we came up the street together: I saw the two prisoners behind the prosecutor and a lady - I saw Watts take the handkerchief out of the prosecutor's pocket; I ran over, seized them both, and called to Hobbs to tell the prosecutor, which he did - I did not see Jones have the handkerchief, but he was close to Watts, and they turned to go away as soon as it was done.</p>
               <p>Jones. Q. Did you see me speak to Watts? A. No.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321018-31-person412">
                  THOMAS 
                  HOBBS
               <interp inst="t18321018-31-person412" type="surname" value="HOBBS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321018-31-person412" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321018-31-person412" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             (Police-constable C 85). I saw the prisoners following the prosecutor - Rice ran and caught hold of them; I saw the handkerchief on the ground.</p>
               <p>Jones. Q. Did I not declare that I did not know this prisoner? A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Watts' Defence. I was going to meet my mother coming home from Newgate-market - I know nothing of Jones.</p>
               <p>Jones' Defence. They did not see me touch the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>WATTS - <rs id="t18321018-31-verdict189" type="verdictDescription">
